listing.description:
APP Kirrane Auctioneering are delighted to offer to the open market 7.7 Acres approx. of development lands (Zoned Residential) located at Cloondace, Knock, Co. Mayo just off the N17 Galway to Sligo main route.

Pre Planning has already taken place P16/22/074 where Mayo County Council have expressed an interest in plots C & D on the attached map being developed for high density mixed residential development with a high percentage 25%-30% of detached dwellings.

 As outlined in the map attached parcel C & D are being sold subject to obtaining planning permission from Mayo County Council these plots could be expanded for recreation or green areas into plots A & B.
There will be an option to purchase the entire plot at an extra cost.

.This development site is in walking  distance of all  Knock village has to offer including shops, public houses, the basilica, post office, restaurants and bus stops. Located just off the N17 within an hours drive of Galway City,  Sligo, Athlone and Ireland West Airport Knock. 

 Part of Folio MY1365.
 
For further information please make contact with the Sole Selling Agents APP Kirrane Auctioneering. APP Kirrane Auctioneering where everything we touch turns to SOLD. 

These particulars are for general information only for this property. The details contained are not to be relied upon as statements or the vendor or representation of fact. Whilst every care is taken in the preparation of the property details, neither APP Kirrane Auctioneering or the vendor or the vendor accept any liability for the details contained in the description of the property. The interested persons must satisfy themselves by viewing the property or employ to inspect the property on their behalf. No Auctioneer or Staff Member employed by APP Kirrane Auctioneering in either Main Street, Ballyhaunis, Co. Mayo or Bohermore, Galway has any authority to make or give any representation or warranty whatever in relation to this property.
